data.description: Welcome home to this immaculate 5 bedroom and 3.5 bathroom house located in Union Station neighborhood. This home features two large primary bedrooms; one located on the main level while the other is located upstairs. The main floor offers a large great room that connects to a formal dining room, a large kitchen with an eat in breakfast area that opens to the family room and a half bath off the kitchen hallway. The first oversized primary bedroom is tucked down a private hall and features a nice en suite with a walk in tub and separate shower. The second floor offers the second oversized primary bedroom with private en suite, a second family room with 3 bedrooms and one full bath. Large flat lot with lots of parking!
